                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1313" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD HOLLIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a farmer, and live in Huntingdonshire. On the 22d of April I was at Greenwich fair—I had a handkerchief fn my pocket—I did not know it was taken, till I was touched on the shoulder—I then looked back, and saw it in the officer's hand—this it—I had it safe in my pocket when I went into the fair.</p>
